{"tid":279871,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[this on9 jai]菲林唔小心放左落托運行李","createTime":"2017-06-11T15:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T14:31:22.000Z","uid":16321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3735755abf6b9e4c01e423a8cdc0e7e4cc5ebe4a","tid":279871,"uid":16321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"喺日本買左四卷菲林<br />\nIso 800 x1<br />\nIso 400 x2<br />\nIso 100 x1<br />\n<br />\n正常hand carry應該就無問題<br />\n但托運x ray好似係勁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知有無人有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪已經玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f60e94e2aa2159056b7412dbac00560a761ab8","tid":279871,"uid":40744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"試過，我啲菲林冇問題"},{"pid":"9c43fac590ae890acda0c4d2feb81f9cf9df12ff","tid":279871,"uid":16321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過，我啲菲林冇問題</blockquote><br />\n800都無事？"},{"pid":"c4992153c1f5c4447ab495ce224dff441edb7342","tid":279871,"uid":14919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"有d難講 不過真係要有心理準備會炒曬<br />\n尤其係800果d"},{"pid":"35e254461191f85f25751fdc32a8e2c04fc4dd27","tid":279871,"uid":16321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d難講 不過真係要有心理準備會炒曬<br />\n尤其係800果d</blockquote><br />\n我諗400/100應該無事掛 見人放instax film都得<br />\n唉800都真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2143bc1f22e105e7ec63296935f1e945d83f1968","tid":279871,"uid":5357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:59: